## PRODUCT STORY CONSTRAINT

> **"The product story is: curated Maximo bot skill packs plus customer-approved evidence produce review-ready delivery intelligence under zero-trust governance. Do NOT rewrite any copy to imply AI replaces the Maximo team."**

Every piece of copy you write or modify must be consistent with this constraint. When in doubt, prefer language that positions MASReady as a **workbench that augments the Maximo delivery team**, not a replacement for it.

