## PART 8: ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA

The implementation is complete only when every criterion below is met. Each criterion is a **hard pass/fail** — no partial credit.

| # | Criterion | Pass Condition |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Skill Coverage framing | The phrase "Skill Coverage" appears nowhere in a people, HR, or team-staffing context in any public-facing file. |
| 2 | Bot skill-pack framing | Every occurrence of "skill coverage" as a metric uses the approved bot skill-pack framing from section 1.2. |
| 3 | 5-layer model | The five-layer model table from section 1.4 is rendered on the `/skills` page or an imported component. |
